    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six. This unit features a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The valvetrain is quiet with documented VANOS maintenance, and the subframe has been reinforced to handle the torsional loads of the chassis. Suspension is composed, utilizing Bilstein dampers for improved rebound control. This is a mechanically sorted example that prioritizes throttle response and lateral grip over showroom aesthetics.",
