      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving mill utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh with Viton seals. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers that preserve the E46's renowned steering feedback. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an excellent entry for the purist seeking an analog performance icon.",
